    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.5-fig1B-note7",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.5",
      "text": "7. Wind speeds correspond to approximately a 15% probability of exceedance in 50 years (Annual Exceedance Probability = 0.00143, MRI = 700 years).",
