    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.5-fig1B-note6",
      "type": "provision",
      "section": "26.5",
      "text": "6. Mountainous terrain, gorges, ocean promontories, and special wind regions shall be examined for unusual wind conditions. Site-specific values for selected special wind regions shall be permitted to be determined using the ASCE Wind Design Geodatabase.",
